{"tid":1744120,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本第一隱乳終於解放！綾瀨遙擠爆F奶領獎","createTime":"2019-11-21T14:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T01:28:48.000Z","uid":9573,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ea78c13363c3b6dce23f2243d77b96547c746b","tid":1744120,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-11-20/900/20191120004796.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-11-20%2F900%2F20191120004796.jpg&h=86f3a0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本當紅女星綾瀨遙被封為演藝圈第一隱乳，為什麼呢？因為她其實擁有F奶超有料的好身材，隨著逐漸在戲劇圈闖出名號，其傲人上圍也逐漸封印起來。不過34歲的她，今(20日)突然在時尚雜誌頒獎典禮大解放，胸前波濤洶湧，預料向西或西南偏西移動，時速約10公里，被日本網友讚爆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-11-20/900/20191120004795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-11-20%2F900%2F20191120004795.jpg&h=087ca722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綾瀨遙罕見爆乳現身。<br />\n<br />\n綾瀨遙今晚在「VOGUE JAPAN WOMEN OF THE YEAR」舉行的頒獎典禮大解放，以一身低胸酒紅色禮服，大膽露出深藏已久的火辣身材，移向呂宋。她還表示非常開心能夠獲獎，未來身為人或女性，都要活出快樂人生。"},{"pid":"d910690651f6a8c704e70cb1f2851c2204c84b83","tid":1744120,"uid":64476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7fddfaab84f0c65ef9449422dbaef26c08217a","tid":1744120,"uid":11154,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:13:05.000Z","msg":"胸前波濤洶湧，預料向西或西南偏西移動，時速約10公里，被日本網友讚爆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3655ec4c3dbb9fdaef4a917cd670b80e8cb8624","tid":1744120,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"搖奶綾"},{"pid":"79109c4500b515925ba4cfed16f20d526e93ba20","tid":1744120,"uid":11254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c7fddf